race.comment: ADMIRE FLUKE (4) brings narrow defeats from Cranbourne on debut and at Wodonga following when he stepped up to this distance backed off the map. Has 22% stable striker Coffey aboard today and fitter he can go one better. WHERE EAGLES DARE (8) is also third-up and will be hard to hold out building on his narrow defeat over 1700m at Warnnambool. Maps for a soft run and will get every chance. ALL THE MOVES (1) can show more third-up and up to the middle distance. He went close at Wodonga over 1250m before the spell and that stacks up. SHARK PARK (11) is in a top metro barn and they are persevering. It won't surprise to see a better effort. CHICKY WA WA (12) peaks and will be around the mark.
